Text:
An exciting upload but deeply flawed.  Comics are repeated with false file names.  Conan the Barbarian #5-#12, for example, are the same comic.  #13-17 then #19 all the way thru #30 are repeats.  #152 and #201 are corrupted files.

That said, there are many good reads in here.
It's a manly download by Crom!

Man, Comcast reported this as a copyright infringement when I downloaded it, so I dumped it. Don't download ANYTHING with Conan The Barbarian attached to it! I thought that since they were comics, then it would be safe to download...NOT! Thanks a lot you sorry ass!
